{
  "name": "zagn8n Approved Content Publisher",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## zagn8n approved content publisher\n\nPurpose:\n- read approved content only\n- turn approved rows into a publishing queue\n- notify you before or when content is queued\n\nRecommended process:\n1. AI workflow generates content\n2. approval-review workflow stores it in the approval queue\n3. you mark rows as `approved`\n4. this workflow reads only approved rows\n5. it forwards them to your publishing queue, Canva prep, or social scheduler\n\nRecommended approval queue sheet columns:\n- generated_at\n- theme\n- instagram_caption\n- tiktok_hook\n- image_headline\n- cta\n- approval_status\n- reviewer_notes\n\nRecommended publish queue sheet columns:\n- queued_at\n- theme\n- channel\n- caption\n- hook\n- headline\n- cta\n- publish_status",
        "width": 640,
        "height": 360
      },
      "id": "3f98b6e3-1f89-4be2-ad50-b2b445d94b05",
      "name": "Setup Notes",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -920,
        -240
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "hours",
              "hoursInterval": 6
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "75e6c6c7-c60e-45b6-8e8b-c7c8ff13e0c3",
      "name": "Queue Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [
        -700,
        160
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "read",
        "documentId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "mode": "id",
          "value": "replace-with-your-google-sheet-id"
        },
        "sheetName": {
          "__rl": true,
          "mode": "name",
          "value": "zagn8n_approval_queue"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "14d5c1b4-6022-46c0-b8e5-91f662ca86df",
      "name": "Read Approval Queue",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets",
      "typeVersion": 4.5,
      "position": [
        -440,
        160
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict",
            "version": 2
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "2cbf3536-2642-4ce3-8cae-1fd2257549e4",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.approval_status }}",
              "rightValue": "approved",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "equals"
              }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "8a573c1e-2ee9-4c0d-86db-e7ea8d03fb56",
      "name": "Approved Only",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        -180,
        160
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "2b513c0f-f30d-418f-a27a-b9ba9c145fac",
              "name": "queued_at",
              "value": "={{ $now.toISO() }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "67681ea2-d422-4e55-ab6d-f7672e32e1b2",
              "name": "channel",
              "value": "instagram_tiktok",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "96ce30d4-98f6-418b-a4c8-20f5b2785113",
              "name": "caption",
              "value": "={{ $json.instagram_caption }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "f7fa8a52-a3dd-4f52-8bca-79dcb2ce84b0",
              "name": "hook",
              "value": "={{ $json.tiktok_hook }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "e6d9d6eb-298c-49db-9943-837d6d1f4200",
              "name": "headline",
              "value": "={{ $json.image_headline }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "4f2de4e2-fd28-40fd-b136-4e7f95b584c1",
              "name": "publish_status",
              "value": "queued",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "07b2d45d-76ff-4e96-9dbe-3f86ed5f6c4d",
      "name": "Prepare Publish Queue Record",
