      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Optional publishing step\n\nAfter `Append Publish Queue`, you can later connect:\n- Canva prep workflow\n- Buffer / Hootsuite / Meta scheduler\n- internal social media queue\n- email approval confirmation",
        "width": 420,
